{"tid":1318576,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你老味大灣暉係信報9up「後物質時代」","createTime":"2019-07-15T03:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T03:52:17.000Z","uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"544d23d30b9a6f9a58b9f6bb1029265a1eb1083f","tid":1318576,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:22:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>一句講曬，乜我地香港嘅年青人而家真係唔在意物質？ Fresh Grad 一出嚟得個萬幾蚊，閒閒地落街食餐晏都要六七十蚊，搭個狗鐵一個廿幾三十蚊不特止仲要成日壞，我都廢事講埋買樓啦。乜呢啲唔係物質咩？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通我可以食咗個IG story 當Lunch？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜鳩「物質時代屬於過去，後物質時代屬於未來，後者數十年內會逐漸成為主流，以有限度的物質衝擊前者，會得到越來越多理解和認同」，「『後物質少年』Vs『物質世代』是永恆的矛盾」，唔該收收皮先啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每日，每一秒，香港人，不止係年青人，都受住唔同程度，唔同方位過嚟嘅壓迫。我地知道唯一可以改變到嘅唔係自己的心態，而係制度本身。我地關心，追求人權，民主，自由唔代表我地唔要物質呀好無？</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌，原文唔貼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己搵啦"},{"pid":"f9ae0b2b92ca08b7b432207397c11002f0148937","tid":1318576,"uid":28914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:24:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b350a4c3319de0c9474c555d67dde376d3e0fb81","tid":1318576,"uid":28451,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:26:27.000Z","msg":"雖然條友係離地，但呢樣野我幫佢口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個term唔係咁解，係academic term黎，有定義"},{"pid":"7256e08914a1c79fbd7d3312f3592eabbb0564cd","tid":1318576,"uid":133183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:27:40.000Z","msg":"現代同後現代都係兩樣野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好按字面解讀"},{"pid":"4edbaa01aacb320f70e6b4ff235bde0de3501dc0",